headline.main: MUSSOLINI WARNS HE WILL CRUSH US; Marks the 19th Anniversary of Fascism by Boasting of Axis Victory MUSSOLINI WARNS HE WILL CRUSH US

lead_paragraph: ROME, Oct. 28 -- On entering the twentieth year of fascism today, Premier Mussolini promised the shattering of "the coalition of bolshevism and its European and American Allies."
abstract: Roosevelt cites German charge he staged incident
